This document guides how to run the test scripts to add/delete flows, meter and
groups.

1) cli-flow-add-del.sh

- Usage
        ./cli-flow-add-del.sh <DPID> <number-of-items> <Add> <Delete> [cli-port]
        DPID             :       Datapath ID
        number-of-items  :       Number of items to be added
        Add              :       0 -No, 1 -Yes
        Delete           :       0 -No, 1 -Yes

    How to run a script to add 1000 flows?
    Example : ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0 10000
                OR
              ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0

    How to run a script to delete 1000 flows?
    Example : ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1 10000
                OR
              ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1

    How to run a script to add 1000 flows and then delete 1000 flows in one go?
    Example : ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1 10000
                OR
              ./cli-flow-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1


2) cli-group-add-del.sh

- Usage
        ./cli-group-add-del.sh <DPID> <number-of-items> <add> <delete> [cli-port]
        DPID             :       datapath id
        number-of-items  :       number of items to be added
        add              :       0 -no, 1 -yes
        delete           :       0 -no, 1 -yes

    How to run a script to add 1000 groups?
    Example : ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0 10000
                or
              ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0

    How to run a script to delete 1000 groups?
    Example : ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1 10000
                or
              ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1

    How to run a script to add 1000 groups and then delete 1000 groups in one go?
    Example : ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1 10000
                or
              ./cli-group-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1

3) cli-meter-add-del.sh

- Usage
        ./cli-meter-add-del.sh <DPID> <number-of-items> <add> <delete> [cli-port]
        DPID             :       datapath id
        number-of-items  :       number of items to be added
        add              :       0 -no, 1 -yes
        delete           :       0 -no, 1 -yes

    How to run a script to add 1000 meters?
    Example : ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0 10000
                or
              ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 0

    How to run a script to delete 1000 meters?
    Example : ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1 10000
                or
              ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 0 1

    How to run a script to add 1000 meters and then delete 1000 meters in one go?
    Example : ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1 10000
                or
              ./cli-meter-add-del.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 1000 1 1

4) cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh

- Usage
        ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh <DPID> <Item> [cli-port]
        DPID             :       Datapath ID"
        Item             :       flow|group|meter"

    How to run a script to count flows?
    Example : ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 flow 10000
                or
              ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 flow 

    How to run a script to count groups?
    Example : ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 group 10000
                or
              ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 group 

    How to run a script to count meters?
    Example : ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 meter 10000
                or
              ./cli-count-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 meter 

 5) cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh

- Usage
        ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh <DPID> <Item> [cli-port]
        DPID             :       Datapath ID"
        Item             :       flow|group|meter"

    How to run a script to show all flows?
    Example : ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 flow 10000
                or
              ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 flow 

    How to run a script to show all groups?
    Example : ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 group 10000
                or
              ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 group 

    How to run a script to show all meters?
    Example : ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 meter 10000
                or
              ./cli-show-flow-meter-group.sh 0xb8ca3a62f674 meter 

            

